data.description: Welcome home to this spacious ranch-style home set on large 100x100 lot in quiet neighborhood with LOW TAXES! Stylish, black-stained wood floors throughout first floor add a touch of elegance to this hard-working space.  Natural maple-colored cabinets with crown-molding in large sun-filled kitchen provide ample storage and counter space for a large family.  Improvements include new CAC system, new oil burner, new insulation in walls, new roof, new front porch & rear patio, double-wide cobblestone-lined driveway.  Finished basement is complete with family rm, finished & unfinished spaces, laundry room, full bath & OSE to yard.  2 finished sheds in yard with electric offer cozy hang-out space & evergreen trees along driveway offer privacy from the neighbors. Fully fenced property and yard is ideal for pets and children.  Let this be your dream home...
